期徒刑；致重傷者，處三年以上十年以下\r\n有期徒刑。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/MLDM/111%2c%e8%8b%97%e4%ba%a4%e7%b0%a1%2c272%2c20220512%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"MLDM,111,苗交簡,272,20220512,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"苗交簡","JNO":"272","JDATE":"20220512","JTITLE":"公共危險"}